      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>4</qty>
          <unit/></amt>
        <item>4-6 oz. beef shell or strip steaks; about 1" thick</item></ing></ingredients>
    <directions>
      <step>  In samll bowl, combine steak sauce, lemon peel, garlic and pepper; brush on
  both sides of steaks. Grill steaks over Medium heat for 15 minutes on each
  side or until done, brushing with sauce occasionally. Serve immediately.
  Serves 4.
  
